      <item>
        <title>Autologin Kicksecure</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Auto login is enabled for me by default for a long time. Re-tested Kicksecure Xfce 15.0.1.9.3 for VirtualBox just now. Works for me.</p>
<p>package:</p>
<aside class="onebox githubfolder">
  <header class="source">
      <img src="https://github.githubassets.com/favicons/favicon.svg" class="site-icon" width="16" height="16">

      <a href="https://github.com/Whonix/vm-config-dist" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com</a>
  </header>

  <article class="onebox-body">
    <img src="https://opengraph.githubassets.com/b85b2f43ff35178db070d3a1bed30e105e54ac2737a37a7800dfb1a4a2dbbdb2/Whonix/vm-config-dist" class="thumbnail onebox-full-image" width="60" height="60">

<h3><a href="https://github.com/Whonix/vm-config-dist" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Whonix/vm-config-dist</a></h3>


  <p><span class="label1">usability enhancements for Debian guest operating systems running inside virtual machines (VMs)</span></p>

  </article>

  <div class="onebox-metadata">
    
    
  </div>

  <div style="clear: both"></div>
</aside>

<p>file:</p>
<aside class="onebox githubblob">
  <header class="source">

      <a href="https://github.com/Whonix/vm-config-dist/blob/master/etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/30_autologin.conf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com</a>
  </header>

  <article class="onebox-body">
    <h4><a href="https://github.com/Whonix/vm-config-dist/blob/master/etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/30_autologin.conf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Whonix/vm-config-dist/blob/master/etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/30_autologin.conf</a></h4>


    <pre><code class="lang-conf">[SeatDefaults]
user-session=xfce
autologin-user=user
</code></pre>



